{"author":{"id":"30a9cdd9e5369167dc36be4d3e5f98e516aa30b7571a17013bc815eef45f09c3"},"ops":[{"type":1,"timestamp":1423073872,"nonce":"SYuDWLi2vhfnjU24XBWpPNbGqEY=","metadata":{"github-id":"MDU6SXNzdWU1NjU2NTgyMQ==","github-url":"https://github.com/galaxyproject/tools-iuc/issues/33","origin":"github"},"title":"IUC Packaging TODO List/Wish List","message":"# Galaxy Tools/Wrappers/Packages\n\nIn the interests of tracking things which we want to package or see included, here's a TODO list for the IUC. These can also make good projects for volunteers :)\n\nPlease feel free to add packages to this list and check them off whenever they get completed!\n## Biological\n- [ ] [RAMPART](https://github.com/TGAC/RAMPART)\n- [x] [Circos](http://circos.ca)\n  - [In Progress](https://github.com/galaxyproject/tools-iuc/tree/circos)\n- [x] [CRAM](https://trello.com/c/0wvdZPud/2016-cram-support) (under tools-devteam)\n- [x] [Phinch](https://github.com/PitchInteractiveInc/Phinch)\n- [ ] [A2m Alignment Format](https://compbio.soe.ucsc.edu/a2m-desc.html) for HMMER\n- [ ] [CONTRAfold](http://contra.stanford.edu/contrafold/)\n- [ ] Some sort of Ontology Browser/Visualizer? I've been testing WebProtege but that's a full featured editor and may be a bit heavy weight for something as simple as .obo viz\n- [ ] [TMPred](http://sourceforge.net/projects/tmpred/)\n- [x] [PEAR](https://github.com/xflouris/PEAR) Done #45 \n- [x] ProgressiveMauve (+ Mauve JS Viz) [WIP](https://github.com/galaxyproject/tools-iuc/tree/mauve)\n- [ ] Sealer/medusa https://github.com/bcgsc/abyss/tree/sealer-release / https://github.com/combogenomics/medusa\n  ### Suites\n- [x] [Seqtk](https://github.com/lh3/seqtk) availability: [MTS](https://toolshed.g2.bx.psu.edu/view/iuc/seqtk)\n- [ ] [GenomeTools](http://genometools.org/tools.html) GFF3 toolkit\n  - [In Progress](https://github.com/erasche/phage-annotation-tools/)\n- [x] [HMMER](http://hmmer.janelia.org/)\n  - [WIP](https://github.com/galaxyproject/tools-iuc/tree/hmmer)\n- [x] QIIME\n  - [existing tools](https://toolshed.g2.bx.psu.edu/view/jjohnson/qiime) that need updates/cleanup. \n  - dunno what [this](https://github.com/qiime/qiime-galaxy) is\n  - [WIP](https://github.com/lparsons/galaxy_tools/tree/qiime/tools/qiime1.9.0)\n- [ ] PacBio Tools\n  - [Progress on BLASR](https://github.com/galaxyproject/tools-iuc/tree/pacbio), and somewhere on my hard drive I had a first stab at converting their workflows to galaxy JSON workflows. Just message me (@erasche) for them.\n## Imaging/Microscopy\n- [ ] FFMpeg for microscopy video data.\n- [ ] ImageMagick's `convert` for imaging data\n  - [progress with support for rotate/flip/format conversion](https://github.com/bgruening/galaxytools/tree/master/tools/image_processing/image_processing)\n- [ ] [CellProfiler](http://www.cellprofiler.org/examples.shtml)\n## Text Analysis\n- [ ] [JsonPath](https://github.com/jayway/JsonPath)\n## Data Sources\n- [ ] [CKAN](http://ckan.org/)","files":null}]}